Dependencies
----------------------------------------------
coldspring 1.2
mxunit 2.0 ( for testing )

Unit test set up
----------------------------------------------
Create a db called books:

CREATE DATABASE `books`
	DEFAULT CHARACTER SET utf8
	DEFAULT COLLATE utf8_general_ci

IF MYSQL MAKE SURE DEFAULT TABLE IS INNODB

Add a dsn called 'books'	

Realease notes
-----------------------------------------------
v. 1.0 
1) Datax does not support orm. 
2) Datax does not support external caching just provides CacheKey hooks.
